<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>keskin uygulama</title>
    <style>
body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background-color: #fafafa;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    height: 100vh;
    margin: 0;
}

.halil{
    text-align: center;
    width: 300px;
    background: #fff;
    padding: 20px;
    border: 1px solid #dbdbdb;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

h1 {
    font-family: 'Grand Hotel', cursive;
    font-size: 36px;
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #8e8e8e;
    margin: 10px 0;
}

.keskin  form {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
}

input {
    padding: 10px;
    border: 1px solid #dbdbdb;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 14px;
}

button {
    padding: 10px;
    background-color: #3897f0;
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: bold;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 14px;
}

button:hover {
    background-color: #3178c6;
}

.celil{
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #8e8e8e;
    margin-top: 15px;
}

.piro-text a {
    color: #3897f0;
    text-decoration: none;
}

.piro a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="halil">
        <h1><i>KESKİN</i></h1>
        <p>Arkadaşlarının fotoğraf ve videolarını görmek için kaydol.</p>
        <div class="keskin">
            <form>
                <input type="text" placeholder="E-posta veya Telefon" required>
                <input type="text" placeholder="Ad Soyad" required>
                <input type="text" placeholder="Kullanıcı adı" required>
                <input type="password" placeholder="Şifre" required>
                <button type="submit">Kaydol</button>
            </form>
        </div>
        <p class="celil">
            Kaydolarak, 
            <a href="#">Koşullarımız</a>
            <a href="#">Gizlilik İlkesi</a> 
            <a href="#">Çerezler Politikamızı</a> 
             kabul etmiş olursun.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>